Package domain.stores.Customer

Class CustomerView

java.lang.Object
domain.stores.Customer.CustomerView
public class CustomerView extends Object
CustomerView represents a read-only view of the data returned from the relationships between Customers, FirstLevelDivisions, and Countries.
Author:
Brandon Epperson
